snippet.textDisplay: I wish Coke Studio would experiment with UP and Bihar’s music outside of Holi too. Especially with Bihar when you have so much diversity in folk music like nirgun, sohar, kajri, chaiti, samdaun etc to name a few. Doing Holi for these states two years in a row is lazy tbh
